# Samasya-Samadhan ğŸŒ

Samasya-Samadhan is an initiative focused on addressing environmental issues and promoting sustainable practices. This platform connects individuals and communities with opportunities to participate in environmental clean-ups, river restoration, farming, and planting activities. Additionally, users can stay informed through the latest news and startup ideas related to sustainability and environmental innovation.

